01:25:35.000 --> 01:25:39.000
of any information system depend on each other.

01:25:39.000 --> 01:25:45.000
In fact, from any small information system, we can create an integrated large system

01:25:45.000 --> 01:25:49.000
that covers the entire enterprise.

01:25:49.000 --> 01:25:56.000
This is evidenced by the development of the history of the business of such companies as HP, Oracle,

