Such a concept of IT technology and IT systems will be useful from another point of view,

01:40:12.000 --> 01:40:20.000
namely, today there is a boom in the development of various IT systems and IT technologies.

01:40:20.000 --> 01:40:26.000
And it is very difficult to understand their differences, to understand the value for business today.

01:40:26.000 --> 01:40:31.000
And since for a certain category of IT specialists and businessmen,

01:40:31.000 --> 01:40:37.000
that is, consultants, experts, vendors, distributors, and other IT systems,

01:40:37.000 --> 01:40:40.000
IT systems are a source of income,

